                            </h1>
                            <p style="color: #718096; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0;">
                                Use the code below to reset your password.
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                        <td align="center" style="padding: 0 40px 40px 40px;">
                            
                            <div style="margin: 30px 0; background-color: #f8fbff; border: 2px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 16px; padding: 25px;">
                                <div style="color: #718096; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.2px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                                    Your OTP is -
                                </div>
                                <div style="color: #007bff; font-size: 42px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 5px; margin: 0;">
                                    {{otp}}
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div style="background-color: #fff5f5; border-radius: 12px; padding: 15px 20px; margin-bottom: 35px; display: table; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;">
                                <p style="color: #c53030; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; margin: 0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                                    ‚ö†Ô∏è Dont share this code with anyone.
                                </p>
                            </div>

                            <a 
                                href="http://localhost:5173/" 
                                target="_blank"
                                style="
                                    background-color: #1a202c; 
                                    color: #ffffff !important; 
                                    text-decoration: none; 
                                    padding: 18px 40px; 
                                    border-radius: 14px; 
                                    display: inline-block; 
                                    font-weight: 700;
                                    font-size: 16px;
                                    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
                                "
                            >
                                Return to Website
                            </a>
